terrific /təˈrɪfɪk/

1. ADJ If you describe something or someone as terrific , you are very pleased with them or very impressed by them. 极好的 [非正式] 

例： What a terrific idea! 多好的主意啊！ 

2. ADJ Terrific means very great in amount, degree, or intensity. 巨大的 [ADJ n] [强调] 

例： All of a sudden there was a terrific bang and a flash of smoke. 忽然发出一声巨响，还冒出一股烟。

